Unikey (Vietnamese Input Method) engine support for Fcitx5

Released under mixed GPLv2+ (main code) and LGPLv2+ (unikey library).

## Dependencies

Required:
- CMake >= 3.6
- Extra CMake Modules (ECM) >= 1.0.0
- Fcitx5 >= 5.1.13
- Gettext
- PkgConfig

Optional (for Qt6 macro/keymap editors):
- Qt6 (Core, Gui, Widgets)
- Fcitx5Qt6WidgetsAddons >= 5.0.12

## Build

    mkdir build && cd build
    cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr ..
    make -j$(nproc)

Or with Ninja:

    mkdir build && cd build
    cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr -G Ninja ..
    ninja

CMake options:
- -DENABLE_QT=On       (default) Build Qt6 macro/keymap editors
- -DENABLE_TEST=On     (default) Build tests
- -DENABLE_COVERAGE=Off          Enable gcov coverage

## Install

    sudo make install

Or with Ninja:

    sudo ninja install

Then restart Fcitx5:

    fcitx5 -r -d

## Uninstall

    sudo make uninstall

Or with Ninja:

    sudo ninja uninstall

## Test

    ctest --test-dir build/
